events.name: ælf - An update on the ælf project
events.description: About the project:aelf is a decentralized self-evolving cloud computing blockchain network that aims to provide a high performance platform for commercial adoption of Blockchain. This keynote serves as an update to the project progress. Find out more here at https://aelf.io/Telegram Group: @aelfblockchain About the speaker:Chen Zhuling,Cofounder / COOA former MIT graduate, consulting veteran at Roland Berger, Zhuling has advised multiple MNCs and governments. Zhuling's exposure at FBG Capital gave him the vantage point of building aelf into a much needed parallel computing platform. Timeline:6:30pm Sign-ups and registration7 - 8:00pm Keynote and Q&A8pm Closing off Thank you Paypal Singapore for the venue sponsor and help! See you there
